				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-466275/scp-1799#post-1438841</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 05 May 2012 13:58:28 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Drewbear</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>301632</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>With the edit on that line (I read it after the edit), I interpreted it to mean that being laughed at actually <em>physically hurts</em> Mr. Laugh. As in, causes him injury and pain. It's happens so very, very often that he's depressedly resigned to it, but it still hurts.</p> 
				 	]]>
