					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-466275#post-1438829</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-466275/scp-1799#post-1438829</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 05 May 2012 13:41:21 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Goodwill</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1124057</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Now that I think about it, making the physical traits more gruesome would be too distracting from the main point. So yeah, I'd agree with downplaying some more while reworking others. Doesn't really matter either way.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-466275#post-1438822</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-466275/scp-1799#post-1438822</link>
