				<wikidot:authorName>TL333s</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1304786</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I was thinking they mostly need to be pared down, especially the limb removal. Out of the four, it's the squirting flower and the cloth trick that stick with me the most. The latter just makes sense as something he'd be able to do; the former could be made into something a little more sinister. (It doesn't squirt water, but something bad; or it's actually attached to his skin and if he doesn't 'release' it occasionally, it causes him great discomfort.)</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
