					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I'm actually not big on this one. The physical feats seem a bit tacked on to fit with the story, and the sad clown thing is kind of predictable. This exchange:</p> <blockquote> <p>SCP-1799:Please…stop laughing at me. It…<br /> (Dr.B███ begins to laugh hysterically, pounding on the table)<br /> SCP-1799: It hurts….my feelings…</p> </blockquote> <p>Is just too silly for me to take this article seriously.</p> 
				 	]]>
